  "response": "Yes, there are several Indian and foreign celebrities who are often noted for their similar appearances. Here are a few examples:\n\n1. **Katrina Kaif and Cobie Smulders**: Katrina Kaif, a well-known Bollywood actress, is often compared to Canadian actress Cobie Smulders, famous for her role in \"How I Met Your Mother.\"\n\n2. **Hrithik Roshan and Bradley Cooper**: Bollywood heartthrob Hrithik Roshan has occasionally been compared to American actor Bradley Cooper due to their similar facial features and build.\n\n3. **Esha Gupta and Angelina Jolie**: Indian actress Esha Gupta has drawn comparisons to Hollywood star Angelina Jolie, especially for their strikingly similar facial features including the lips and eyes.\n\n4. **Parineeti Chopra and Hayden Panettiere**: Some observers have noted a resemblance between Bollywood actress Parineeti Chopra and American actress Hayden Panettiere.\n\n5. **Jiah Khan and Anne Hathaway**: Late Bollywood actress Jiah Khan was often compared to American actress Anne Hathaway for their similar facial structures.\n\nThese comparisons are often made based on certain photographs or specific angles, and similarities can be subjective.",
